how to find the nodes that run currentlly:
ros2 node list

to get the info about the node use:
ros2 node info     

to see all the topic options use:
ros2 topic


how listen to the state of the drone use:
ros2 topic echo /multicopter001/gimbal/state

to listen to the orientation use: (roll,pitch,yaw)
ros2 topic echo /multicopter001/arena/set_state
